00:13:00.250 --> 00:13:01.490
Sensei!

00:13:01.490 --> 00:13:04.560
Am-ambulans!

00:13:05.930 --> 00:13:10.680
Nanatsutake Hastanesi

00:13:10.680 --> 00:13:14.680
Handa Sei  
Özel Oda

00:13:11.190 --> 00:13:14.680
Sıcak çarpması, uykusuzluk, iştahsızlık...

00:13:15.460 --> 00:13:17.420
